description: Punk's Chicken Shack throws a picnic party with fried chicken, drinks, and all the fixins’ in a classic Southern way to give you an event that goes from casual to corporate, without the fuss.Biscuits, mashed potatoes, and collard greens come straight from the kitchen of Punk’s Simple Southern Food in Rice Village and your chicken is fried up fresh to order.Go all out with snacks like Deviled Eggs, Pimento Cheese and Sweet Corn Hushpuppies, or load up your table with all the fixins’ from Macaroni N’ Cheese to Creamed Corn. Sports fanatics top off their game day with wings tossed in Mango Habanero BBQ, while parents please their lil’ birds with a boneless bird and some fries. Punk’s Chicken Shack Catering Truck gives you a Southern picnic with all the charm. Now come out and party!
name: Punk’s Chicken Shack Catering Truck
